quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  16,22,UMvelinqangi wenu uMvelinqangi oyedwa vo ngakho- ke labo abangakholelwa empilweni ezayo izinhliziyo zabo ziyakwenqaba (lokho) futhi bona bayazigabisa
  16,23,Akungabazeki ukuthi uMvelinqangi uyakwazi lokho abakufihlayo kanye nalokho abakuvezayo ngempela yena akabathandi abazigabisayo
  16,24,"Futhi uma (bebuzwa) kuthiwa kubona yini eyembulwa iNkosi yena na? bathi, “izinganekwane zabantu basendulo”"
  16,25,Ukuze bakwazi ukuthwala imithwalo yabo yonke ngelanga lokuvuka kwabafileyo kanye nemithwalo yalabo ababadukisa ngaphandle kolwazi ngokungangabazeki kubi lokho abayokuthwala